Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就不该把他带回来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Should've never brought him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道自己在干什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I know what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可不  你一直这么说\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah, you keep saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,达里尔\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Daryl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是你吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人呢  他们还好吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The others? Are they okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你的朋友们在哪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I don't know where your friends are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不在乎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I don't care, neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-但是...  -没什么可但是的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- But I -- - But nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不过是分享过食物而已\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Just 'cause we shared a bag of grain
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这不意味着我在乎你们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}does not make me give a shit about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,听明白了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,无论你们和这帮人有什么过节\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Whatever beef you have with these people,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不想掺和\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I want no part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,听见了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好闭上嘴  别来烦我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You need to shut up and leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,懂了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,懂了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I got it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我没看错你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I was right about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,当初就应该让你饿着\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Shoulda let you starve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,王八蛋\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我一个字都不会透露给你们的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I ain't telling you bastards a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,起来  起来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Get up. Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,和从前一样固执\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Just as stubborn as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是这么认为的吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Is that what you think this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我固执\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Me being stubborn?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是坚韧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Hard-headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你得把真相告诉我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You need to tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没有骗过你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I've never lied to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,从来没有  莉娅\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Never, Leah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,现在也不会\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm not gonna start now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们再试一遍\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Let's try this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,关于那群人  你都了解些什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What do you know about those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都不了解\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I don't know shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我可以  我肯定会帮你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'd help you if I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我会的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You know I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,把狗还给我  放我走吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Just give me Dog, let me go,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你再也不会见到我了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}you'll never see me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你想要的吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Is that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.08,0:17:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,找到博西了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Found Bossie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,特纳呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And Turner?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我努力过了  但没能救他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I tried. I couldn't save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-我努力过了  -没关系  孩子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- I tried. - It's okay, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你做了正确的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You did the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你把他带回家了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You brought him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,主啊  我们把兄弟特纳交给你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Lord, we release our brother Turner to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,请您拥紧他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Please, hold him close.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,以主之名  阿门\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}In your name, oh Lord, amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,阿门\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝在此\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}God is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他很愤怒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He's angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我很愤怒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你们感受到了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Do you feel that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,去让他们感受到我们的怒火\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Go make them feel our wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一个兄弟死了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}One of my brothers is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫迈克尔·特纳\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Michael Turner was his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们曾在世界各地并肩战斗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We fought all over the world together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最后一次驻扎回来后  教皇将他纳入麾下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Pope brought him in after our last tour,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那时他刚创办公司\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}when he started his company.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你们是士兵\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I thought you were soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们曾经是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We were.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,之后私营化了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Then we went private.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你之前没告诉过我你是佣兵\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You didn't tell me you were a merc.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这重要吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Mm, does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,都是一样的工作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I mean, it's the same damn job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,只是我们真能付得起生活费了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Except we could actually pay our bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔跟我很像  他也没有家人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Michael was like me, you know? He didn't have a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是我没能拥有的弟弟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He was the little brother I never had.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直想要的弟弟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You know, the little brother I always wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.31,0:21:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他死了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这里失去过很多同伴\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You know, we lost a lot of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一直很艰难\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}here, and it's been hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但这次不一样\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Not like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This is the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,很长时间以来第一次失去了亲近的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I've lost someone close to me in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,或许除了你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}except maybe for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你那时并没失去我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You didn't lose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我回去找过你  但你走了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I came back and you were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你离开了我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.39,0:22:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我问你你想要什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I asked you what you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你就走了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You left.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我害怕了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I got scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,怕什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,放手\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Letting go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.47,0:22:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,无所谓了  反正我们也不会有结果\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It doesn't matter. It wouldn't have worked anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.56,0:22:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能拥有幸福\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Couldn't have been happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.02,0:22:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,在这样一个世界里不可能\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Not in a world like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.73,0:23:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的想法还是你家人的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Is that you talking or your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.52,0:23:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你就没做过坏事吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Like you've never done things?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,杀人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Killed people.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你做过什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I know the things you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.61,0:23:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你没权利指责我  根本没有\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You have no right to judge, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.95,0:23:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是真正的我  达里尔\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This is me, Daryl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不论是好的还是坏的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The good and the bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是我  一直如此\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}All of it. It always has been.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.71,0:23:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.76,0:23:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也没办法\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, I can't help with that.
