Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.99,0:33:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为这就结束了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, and you think that's the end of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.75,0:33:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你还想要我做什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What else do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.67,0:33:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.92,0:33:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要你理解\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I want you to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.52,0:33:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,坐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.48,0:33:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都是在死亡谷认识的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We all met in the Valley of Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.82,0:33:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,反正我们是这样称呼那里的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That's what we call it, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.66,0:33:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,阿富汗的山区\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Hills of Afghanistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.24,0:33:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为国奋战\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We fought for our country,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.33,0:33:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,把阵亡的战友抬下战场\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}carried our fallen brothers off the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.37,0:33:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,抬了太多人  后来我们都数不清了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Carried so many, we lost count after a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.42,0:33:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,政客们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Politicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.38,0:33:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,只管开支票\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They wrote the checks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.47,0:34:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,根本不在乎我们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We weren't anything to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.35,0:34:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是道具\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Just props.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.39,0:34:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,下次竞选所用的道具\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Props for their next campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.81,0:34:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们喜欢谈论上帝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}See, they -- they talked about God.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.94,0:34:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不认识上帝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They didn't know God.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.15,0:34:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没见过他的脸\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They never saw His face.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.19,0:34:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不像我们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's not like we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.24,0:34:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们看到上帝无处不在\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We saw God everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.41,0:34:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他在鲜血  恐怖和死亡之中\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He was in the blood and the horror and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.41,0:34:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他在那  为我们指引方向\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He was there, telling us where to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.25,0:34:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在那段日子里  我们唯有指望他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Didn't have much else to hold on to in those days but Him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.51,0:34:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,还有彼此\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.97,0:34:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你抽烟吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.32,0:35:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那场战争差点永远废了我们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That war damn near ruined all of us for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.62,0:35:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,回国之后  我的部下都有永久性损伤\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Came home and my guys had permanent injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.41,0:35:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他们睡不着觉  找不到正经工作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They couldn't sleep. They couldn't find real jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.13,0:35:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.63,0:35:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们成了人们口中的佣兵\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}people called us mercenaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.68,0:35:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那些没人想做的脏活累活\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We did all the ugly, dirty work
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.14,0:35:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,都由我们来做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}nobody else wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.31,0:35:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,还拿到了丰厚的佣金\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Got paid for it, too. Handsomely.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.36,0:35:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真正的脏活是在沦陷之后开始的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The real dirty work started after the Fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.91,0:35:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没有经历过那样的战争\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Never been in a war like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.00,0:35:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,从没有见过那样的混乱\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Never seen that kind of chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.54,0:35:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,而我以前什么都见过\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and I had seen everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.17,0:36:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但这个\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But this...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.68,0:36:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们做的那些事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, the things we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.52,0:36:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的死亡  日复一日\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}All that death, day after day after day...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.52,0:36:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不久以后  我和你有了同样的想法\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}After a while, I started to feel like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.82,0:36:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想  上帝哪去了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Wondering -- Wondering where God was.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.70,0:36:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,直到他再次现身\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Until He showed His face again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.87,0:36:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,政客们  还有最后一场仗要打\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}See, politicians -- they had one last war to get behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.42,0:36:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这一次  敌人是我们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This time, coming for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.46,0:36:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,炸弹如暴雨般落下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The bombs came thick and fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.34,0:36:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一直没有停\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It did not stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.43,0:36:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们和一些战友走散了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We lost some of our own,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.56,0:36:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不得不穿越大火去救他们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}had to run through the fire to save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.19,0:36:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在城镇边缘找到了一座小教堂\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Found this little church at the edge of town,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.48,0:36:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们躲在那里  看着一切\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and we holed up there as everything --
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.19,0:37:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说所有的一切  在身边燃烧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and I mean everything -- burned around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.91,0:37:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,等火终于熄灭了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}When the fires finally died down,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.58,0:37:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我看向我的部下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I looked at my people...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.71,0:37:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我简直不敢相信\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I could not believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.13,0:37:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,没留一滴血\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Not a trace of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.38,0:37:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,没有烧伤\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No burn marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.22,0:37:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,连擦伤都没有\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Not even a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.76,0:37:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那时我就知道了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And that's when I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.35,0:37:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是天选之人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We were the Chosen Ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.15,0:37:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}These men --
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.19,0:37:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,火焰伤不了这些人的身躯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}These men upon whose bodies the fire had no power.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.08,0:37:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝今晚选中了你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}God chose you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.17,0:38:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你毫发无伤  活着逃出了火场\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I mean, you -- you came out of that fire alive and whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.01,0:38:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你  现在坐在这里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And look at you now, sitting right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.47,0:38:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你受伤了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.14,0:38:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,被烧到了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Any burns?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.47,0:38:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,有擦伤吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}A scratch?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.10,0:38:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前经历过更糟的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I've been through worse before.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.99,0:38:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你饿吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Are. You. Hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.07,0:39:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.11,0:39:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,关于这家伙\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}About this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.44,0:39:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然对了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Of course I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.28,0:39:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,分他点  博西\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Give him some, Bossie.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.20,0:39:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,别太贪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Don't be greedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.83,0:39:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在是家人了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He's family now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.59,0:39:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他做了什么吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You know what he did, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.47,0:39:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他背着死去的兄弟走了10英里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He walked 10 miles with his dead brother on his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.60,0:39:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,10英里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}10 miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.64,0:39:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这需要多大的力量啊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The strength that took...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.48,0:39:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我们有多感激吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You have any idea how grateful we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.15,0:39:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,特纳会有一个体面的葬礼\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Turner will have a proper burial.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.57,0:39:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是做了我们都会做的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Just did what any one of us would've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.50,0:40:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还疼吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}These still hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.09,0:40:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,需要什么吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You need anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.05,0:40:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想问一个问题\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I just have one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.10,0:40:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.48,0:40:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,有件事我一直很困惑\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Something's been bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.06,0:40:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你的伤口\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Your wounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.61,0:40:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在背上\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}are on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.82,0:40:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,教皇  今天已经够辛苦了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Pope, it's been a rough day.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.90,0:40:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想弄清楚  肖\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Just getting clarity, Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.03,0:40:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,特纳被袭击时  你在哪里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Where were you when Turner was being attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.04,0:40:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我在现场  我给你说过了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I-I was right there, just like I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.08,0:40:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,面朝敌人吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Facing the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.42,0:40:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.42,0:40:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他受的苦够多了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He's been through enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.97,0:41:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕了会跑是人的本能反应\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Human nature is to run when you are scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.23,0:41:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You know what that's like, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.57,0:41:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,直面恐惧需要非凡的勇气\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It takes divine strength to face your fear head-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.28,0:41:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,为别人赌上一切\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Risk everything for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.04,0:41:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都看到了你所做的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We all saw what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.66,0:41:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,先把肖救出火场  你也感受到了吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Getting Shaw out of the fire first, and you felt it, huh?
